==English==
===Etymology===
Greek (''hēdonē''), meaning ''pleasure.'' (Eng. usg. 1856)
===Noun===
'''hedonism'''
# The belief that [[pleasure]] is the only [[worthwhile]] pursuit in [[life]].
# A lifestyle based on or implying hedonism (as par definition #1).

